column288: Open Questions: 1. Please describe your food habits when you are feeling anxious or depressed
column289: 2. Please describe in a couple paragraphs your exercise patterns when you are feeling anxious or dep...
i don't exercise when i feel anxious

Formerly, would try to get exercise (usually raquetball) when feling depressed, and it seemed to help me feel better. However, over the last few years, I've developed arthritis (mostly lower back) that limits my physical activities to mostly short walks, and picking some fruit (blackberries, apples) in our back yard.
